-- Hamilton Wins Italian Grand Prix, McLaren’s 3rd Straight Victory
-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 2012-09-09T13:24:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-09/hamilton-wins-italian-grand-prix-mclaren-s-3rd-straight-victory.html
Lewis Hamilton  won today’s Italian
Grand Prix at Monza to give his McLaren team a third straight
Formula One victory.   Hamilton, the 2008 world champion, finished ahead of
Sauber’s Sergio Perez and Ferrari’s Fernando Alonso -- the
championship leader.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Cone at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  